longest_rain.status: The storm today ranked 5th for the length of the storm when compared to others in our records and it lasted 22.9 hours.  7.68mm of rain fell and at one point was falling at 4.1mm per hour.  On 04 January 2025, the rain lasted for 37.2 hours, which is the longest time recorded by our database.  36.8mm accumulated and it fell at 4.6mm per hour at times.
